Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.32,0:00:02.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.08,0:00:06.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everybody, don't ya want \NSensei to come back real soon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.43,0:00:08.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.42,0:00:13.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so that Sensei can come back at any time,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:17.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we're gonna clean this room up good!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.04,0:00:18.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:21.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost all of the mess was made by Miwa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.49,0:00:23.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let her fool you, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:26.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, hop to it! Do it for Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.31,0:00:29.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:36.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder when Sensei's comin' back...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.96,0:00:38.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, when...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.33,0:00:45.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.20,0:00:49.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry on back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:54.49,MX Calligraphy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&H98453C&}You Shouldn't Go \NBack to the Island
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:56.99,MX Calligraphy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18\c&H98453C&}You Shouldn't Go Back to the Island
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.05,0:00:59.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:18.65,Barakamon Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Barakamon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.02,0:02:36.01,MX Calligraphy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\c&H98453C&}You Shouldn't Go \NBack to the Island
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:33.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:36.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:42.51,MX Calligraphy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18\c&H98453C&}You Shouldn't Go Back to the Island
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:37.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.93,0:02:41.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,this is my silent protest to prevent \Nyou from going back to the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:42.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Silent"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:45.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I submitted my calligraphy for the exhibition,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:47.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of going home to the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.65,0:02:49.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Going home"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.59,0:02:51.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Home is {\i1}here{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:52.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The island is "away"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:54.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You ungrateful son!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.85,0:02:55.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:02:57.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:03:00.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep punching until you say you won't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:01.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:03.76,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it! Punch! Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:03.76,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This actually kind of hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:06.39,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't stop until you say it! Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:06.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:07.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawafuji-kun is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.86,0:03:09.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawafuji-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:10.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawafuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:11.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:15.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just came to report that your work for \Nthe exhibition was delivered safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:17.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:19.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not interrupting anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:21.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go eat out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to run, Sei-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:26.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't leave this matter unsettled!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.41,0:03:27.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all think about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.11,0:03:30.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawafuji-kun, please help to persuade him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:35.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was against this from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:40.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then I had no choice, since my \Nhusband made the decision on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:42.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, later, I found out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.04,0:03:45.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,that you'd fallen ill and gone to the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:49.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And we were always so careful about \Nyour cat allergy while you were here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:50.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:53.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I restrain you, \Nyou'll still insist on going, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:56.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I won't ask your opinion!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:03:59.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep you from leaving, even \Nif I have to resort to house arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:02.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom's really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:05.09,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's finally putting her foot down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:08.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think her argument is sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:09.22,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:12.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Aren't you on {\i1}my{\i0} side?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:16.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we know you can write \Ncalligraphy even in Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:19.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you working hard instead \Nof lounging around on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:23.36,Factions,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(315,1)}Opposing Faction
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:23.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the system we're following?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:29.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,True, it's easy to think of an isolated island \Nas a backwoods place without electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:30.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:35.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just by living away from the mainland, \Nyou can find what you need to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:39.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There, a shut-in like me can live life to the fullest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:46.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have few friends here, anyway. \NAll that matters is that I can write calligraphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:47.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:49.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listening to him is making me sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:52.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think my worries are only about the land?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:58.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mixing with strange people, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:02.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your speech and mannerisms have turned crude.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.91,0:05:04.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were never like that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:07.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have I really gotten that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:10.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, not so much bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.34,0:05:11.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,as weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:13.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lie down with dogs, and you'll get up with fleas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:15.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Choose your companions more carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:18.44,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,"Lie down with dogs, and you'll get up with fleas"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:24.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not! I'm not! I'm not! I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:26.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:28.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been behaving strangely since you returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:30.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You gorge yourself on pickled vegetables
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:33.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and say odd words like "komonno" and "nusano"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.49,0:05:34.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been influenced at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:38.19,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:41.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You never used to make such a fuss, Sei-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:47.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're worried about the land or his character,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:50.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't expect there will be any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:53.45,Factions,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,1)}Supporting Faction
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.02,0:05:53.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, you're following this system, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:56.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was around Seishuu's age,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:58.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I also stayed on that island.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:05:59.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no issue with the environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:01.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You lived on the island, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:04.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't been there myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:06.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have forced you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:09.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasn't Kido Yuujirou taken good care of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:10.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kido...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:12.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The village chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:13.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:17.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe I have an old album \Nof photographs from that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:18.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:20.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning to tip the odds in your favor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.18,0:06:23.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll only reminisce a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:32.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew you had old photographs like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:35.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seimei-sensei, you look just like Handa here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:37.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes don't look as mean as his.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.49,0:06:39.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:41.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A photo from when I was on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.27,0:06:45.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, the village chief looks so young!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:47.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was about thirty-five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.48,0:06:49.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to catch a "hisan iwo" with Kido.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:51.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hisan iwo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:52.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! "Nusano"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:55.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We caught a hisan iwo, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:57.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wouldn't say "caught"...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:07:00.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Is this the Kinoshita General Store?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:02.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I believe that was the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:04.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the shopkeeper?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:06.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look how young she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:08.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She really was pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:09.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! This river's still there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:12.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I once hurt myself there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:14.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too! I still have the scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.13,0:07:18.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All you're talking about is the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:21.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,None of you understand how I feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:23.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've been so worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:26.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're being too irresponsible, Daa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:29.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your precious son is walking \Ndown the path to ruin here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:31.19,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Daa-chan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:32.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:35.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If children grow through \Nseparation from their parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:36.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then this is for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:39.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you on my side, Daa-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:45.77,Mom1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(180,1)}Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:45.77,Mom2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(180,1)}Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:45.77,Mom3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(180,1)}Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:43.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were always frail and sickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.24,0:07:45.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you abandon me \Nafter all I did for you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:48.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your ingratitude is like a mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:50.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom's a real pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:53.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you all belittle \Na mother's feelings like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:55.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She heard me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:57.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your ingratitude is like the wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:00.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:02.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, hey! Ma'am, that hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:04.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kawafuji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:08.94,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I won't be able to go back for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:09.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seishuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:14.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I may have sent you to the island initially,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:15.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but now it's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:20.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always free to come home once you're \Nsatisfied with your calligraphy style.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:23.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You decide what to do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:32.28,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,I have wished for nothing but the best for Sei-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:35.24,MX Calligraphy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}You Shouldn't Go Back to the Island
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:37.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've done the calligraphy for the exhibit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:39.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and I've gotten some idea of my direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:42.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's no need to \Nrush back to the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:44.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll be a shut-in no matter where you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:47.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it'd be more convenient to stay in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:53.22,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it, Tokyo is better...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:55.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So why am I stressing over it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:08:58.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sei-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:01.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A package arrived for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:04.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to be from the islanders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:09.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this package mean that \Nthey don't want you to return?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:11.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:13.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was struggling with the exhibition,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:17.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked them to send some materials I needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:19.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:21.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:24.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They just packed all kinds of crap in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:25.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bullying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:28.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My son is being bullied!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:29.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:32.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be Naru's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:35.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?! Who is this "Naru"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.18,Tama package,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Sensei,\NI won a gold prize.\NNext is the prefectural \Ncompetition!    Tama
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:39.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:41.01,Miwa package,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a silver prize.\NCurse you, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:44.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They even sent me this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:45.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sei-san, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:48.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The practice writings from the \Nkids I was teaching on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:53.82,MX Calligraphy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}Learning From the Past\N\NClass 2-1 Yamamura
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:53.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They made great progress in \Npractically no time at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:57.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd known their penmanship projects \Nwould be graded that soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.42,0:09:59.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've waited to see them before coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.27,0:10:03.22,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have received the results with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:06.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so I could encourage them and celebrate with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:10.58,Don't Go,,0000,0000,0000,,You Shouldn't Go \NBack to the Island
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:08.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sei-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:15.67,MX Calligraphy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&H98453C&}You Shouldn't Go \NBack to the Island
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:19.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:21.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, are you going to sulk again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.21,0:10:23.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sulking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:25.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If they need you there,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:28.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then you have to go back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.34,0:10:30.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:34.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just make sure to call us regularly this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:40.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she... telling me I can go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:49.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:50.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:54.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That boy honestly wants to \Ndo something for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:57.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Keeping him longer would \Nonly be selfish on my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:01.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't just his calligraphy that's matured.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:06.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That island is a good place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:09.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we visit there before it gets cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:10.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:19.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:25.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not long ago, we received word from \Nour village phone watchman, Akki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:28.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, Sensei is coming back on the evening flight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:30.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:31.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And so!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:35.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the day we're gettin' \Nthis house cleaned up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:36.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:40.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei really will be mad if he comes \Nhome to this, so let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:44.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, this is heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:47.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First Sensei leaves the island without warnin',
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:50.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and now he's comin' back without warnin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:53.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are those guys cleanin' the place up right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:58.32,MX Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,tick tick tick tick tick tick
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.93,0:12:16.79,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined we'd waste so much time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:18.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.03,0:12:19.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-nii! When did you get here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:21.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:22.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:26.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We learned the hard way it's no fun \Nonce the excitement's worn off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:28.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make us feel worse'n we already do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.39,Battle,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.77,0:12:31.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I shoulda known you kids couldn't handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.95,0:12:34.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya ain't cleaned nothin' at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:34.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tee-hee!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:36.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "tee-hee" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:38.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-nii, what are you here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:40.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's gonna be gettin' cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:42.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd put up the windows at Sensei's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:46.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, there \Nain't no windows here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:48.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We took 'em down and put 'em in our shed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:50.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so the glass wouldn't break in a typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:54.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll direct everyone, so clean up right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:56.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:59.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta hurry. Sensei's on his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:00.55,Burnable,,0000,0000,0000,,Need               Don't Need \N{\fs22}Burnable      Non-burnable
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:00.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Separate the trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:02.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, you sweep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:02.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayup!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:04.76,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys wipe down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:10.22,Trash Bag,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotou City{Designated?}\N{\fs14}Burnable Trash \NCollection Bag
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:07.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The place is lookin' a lot cleaner, Hiro-nii.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:08.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you guys to work, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:10.22,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave any trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:12.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, yer inflexible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:15.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all for Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:17.19,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For Sensei, for Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:19.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:20.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:22.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.25,0:13:23.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:25.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:29.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:30.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:33.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much room now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:36.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can make all kinds'a mess in here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:38.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What worries me is that she'd really do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:41.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we just wait for Sensei to come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:43.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:44.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:46.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll go home and fetch some snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:49.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-nii, go make some food to bring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:51.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya really do wanna mess up the room again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:00.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:09.78,Fukue Airport,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukue Airport
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:08.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The village chief's supposed to come get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:13.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll probably bump into him if I start walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:22.42,MX Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging \NRoom
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.49,0:14:22.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seishuu-kun's calligraphy should be soon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.73,0:14:23.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:26.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen it yet myself, \Nso I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.85,0:14:29.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzaki-kun's calligraphy was wonderful as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.67,0:14:32.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so this may be another battle \Nbetween the two young rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.15,0:14:35.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than focus on the immediate results,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:39.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope my son will accept them and \Nlook ahead to what comes next.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:44.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that Seishuu-kun is behaving \Nwith sufficient thought for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:47.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that he's had plenty of painful experiences,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:50.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,he should behave less impulsively from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:55.58,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He should behave less impulsively, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:57.46,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I do hope so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:03.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Village chief... You're still not here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:05.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! A vending machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:07.76,Impulse,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(230,1)}Impulse
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:11.22,Pain1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(230,1)}Painful \NExperience
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:13.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quick! Just need my wallet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:16.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My money!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:17.81,Pain2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(230,1)}Painful\NExperience
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:20.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Got the coins... Now, cold tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:22.44,Cold - Hot,,0000,0000,0000,,Cold                         {\3c&H232AAA&}Hot
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:22.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:23.94,Tea,,0000,0000,0000,,Green\NTea
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:25.69,Corn,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot 'n'\NHearty\NCorn
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:25.69,Pain1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(230,1)}Painful \NExperience
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:28.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it too early to have winter items?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:34.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:37.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:39.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're ya doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.15,0:15:41.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to pick me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:43.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, just out fer a drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the village chief doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:47.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:49.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna hop on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:02.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, this is just \Nhow it was when I first arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:03.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, right about now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:15.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather's good today, so it's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.23,0:16:19.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just th' ocean. Ain't nothin' special.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:22.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing special, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:27.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's best when there's nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:31.26,Phone Note,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a call \Nfrom Kawamoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:35.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, this is the Kinoshita General Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:37.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kawafuji-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:40.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe Sensei should already be home...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:42.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The village chief was going to—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:43.87,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, is 'round here fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:44.62,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:45.66,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.66,0:16:47.73,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,'Round here fine by you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:48.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:48.23,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:48.83,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:50.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.77,0:16:59.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment Sensei opens the front door,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:01.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll give 'im a big cheer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:02.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna do a tackle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:04.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:07.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:10.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:11.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "just" me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:12.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:16.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawafuji-san called for him, so he's at the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:18.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the results of that \Ncalligraphy exhibition are out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:20.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, really? That was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:21.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This could be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:22.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:25.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be depressed if he got second place again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:26.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.36,0:17:30.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei's a grown man, so he ain't gonna \Nsay anything to spoil the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:32.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're naïve, Hiro-nii!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:34.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't underestimate Sensei's childishness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:37.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make light of how \Nmortifyin' second place is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:40.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone! Sensei's comin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:41.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's my cracker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:43.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you have it just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:45.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, mine's gone, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:46.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's mine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:50.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Found 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:51.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.65,0:18:05.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't no laughin' matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:06.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:08.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:11.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are treating me like this \Nafter I was gone all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:13.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:15.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hands are all sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:17.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:19.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, we oughta be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:20.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:22.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd the calligraphy competition go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:24.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did ya get first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:29.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru! Didn't we tell ya not to ask that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.34,0:18:31.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a very delicate subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:32.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:34.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, don't worry 'bout it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:38.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, were you guys concerned about \Nthe results of the calligraphy exhibition?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:41.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did ya place well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:43.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.61,0:18:45.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! You done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:45.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:46.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:47.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:54.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.49,0:18:56.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The old veterans were just too good this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:19:02.07,Results,,0000,0000,0000,,Results
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:19:02.07,Names,,0000,0000,0000,,5. Handa Sei\N\N7. Kanzaki Kousuke
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:18:59.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were both out of the running.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:02.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They probably didn't want the \Nyoungsters to get swelled heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:05.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is more like the result \Nyou should have had the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.97,0:19:08.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're here, Kawafuji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:10.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.09,0:19:12.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You informed Seishuu of the results?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:15.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he seemed concerned about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.29,0:19:19.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that it was \Na depressing result for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.98,0:19:22.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's hard to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:26.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, this was his first step in \Nwriting with his own calligraphy style.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:28.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to his future work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.91,0:19:32.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:35.22,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what kinda calligraphy did ya write, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:36.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm curious, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:39.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The theme wasn't anything major.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:41.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit bein' so coy and just tell us! \NYa placed well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:46.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya could at least say that much, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:47.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.59,0:19:49.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'd say,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:52.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it's about what's most important to me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:57.96,MX Calligraphy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}Kido Hiroshi     Yamamura Miwa    Kubota Hina
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:57.96,MX Calligraphy,,0000,0000,0000,,Arai Tamako                Kotoishi Naru
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:54.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's most important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:57.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it's Hiro-nii!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.56,0:19:57.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't it the penmanship we wrote?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:58.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:20:02.68,Naru,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotoishi \NNaru
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:01.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys're so shallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.29,0:20:02.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,People run on food!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:06.30,Miwa,,0000,0000,0000,,Kido            Yamamura                            Kubota \NHiroshi            Miwa                                    Hina
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:06.30,Tama,,0000,0000,0000,,Arai\NTamako
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:04.65,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't about food, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:06.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, maybe a rabbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:08.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.51,0:20:10.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's rhinoceros beetles!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:11.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's a praying mantis!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.93,0:20:13.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My bet's on scorpions!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:15.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put Sensei on the spot, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:18.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aki, you're playing the "good boy" role again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.14,0:20:19.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:21.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gone cold, Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:23.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:24.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:28.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An awful lot's happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:30.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's real fun when we're all together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:41.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I see you guys having fun \Nwith no thought for anything else,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:43.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it has an influence on me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:45.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"In-flew-ants"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:52.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It means these are the moments \Nthat are important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.26,0:20:54.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:57.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:06.20,Barakamon Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,700)}Kaette Kite \NUrishika
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:09.95,Barakamon Title 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,1)}Glad You're Back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:09.95,Naru Stamp,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:50.01,End Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad You're Back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:50.01,End Sign 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustration: Tachibana Masaki
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.54,0:22:42.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, set...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.10,0:22:45.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
